<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="app-allsupp" xml:lang="en">
    <head>Appendix: All Supporting Data Guidelines</head>

    <list>
        <head><ref target="supp-structure.html">Structure of an EpiDoc edition</ref></head>
        <item>See below for detailed guidance on individual elements</item>
    </list>

    <div>
        <head>Physical description and history of text-bearing object</head>
        <list>
            <head><ref target="supp-description.html">Physical description</ref></head>
                <item><ref target="supp-descobject.html">Description and dimensions of monument or object</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-desctext.html">Description and layout of text field or campus</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-descdimensions.html">Dimensions (of object or campus)</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-descdecor.html">Decoration or iconography</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-descletters.html">Description of letters or hands</ref></item>
        </list>
        <list>
            <head><ref target="supp-history.html">History and locations</ref></head>
                <item><ref target="supp-historigdate.html">Date of origin</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-histinvno.html">Inventory numbers and repository</ref></item>
                <item><ref target="supp-histlocations.html">Locations</ref>:
                    <list>
                    <item><ref target="supp-historigin.html">Original location or locations</ref></item>
                    <item><ref target="supp-histfound.html">Place and context of finding</ref></item>
                    <item><ref target="supp-histmodern.html">Last known location, other modern locations</ref></item>
                    </list>
                </item>
        </list>
    </div>

    <div>
        <head>Other commentary and documentary sections of the edition</head>
        <list>
            <item><ref target="supp-apparatus.html">External apparatus criticus</ref></item>
            <item><ref target="supp-translation.html">Translation</ref></item>
            <item><ref target="supp-commentary.html">Commentary (line-by-line or introductory)</ref></item>
            <item><ref target="supp-bibliography.html">Bibliography</ref></item>
            <item><ref target="supp-images.html">Figures or facsimile</ref></item>
        </list>
    </div>
    
    <div>
        <head>Metadata</head>
        <list>
            <item><ref target="supp-publication.html">Title and publication information</ref></item>
            <item><ref target="supp-languages.html">Languages and scripts</ref></item>
        </list>
    </div>

    <div>
        <head>Indexing terms in the text (words, names, places, keywords)</head>
        <list>
            <item>Words and lemmatization</item>
            <item>Personal names and prosopography</item>
            <item>Place names and geographical terms mentioned in the text</item>
            <item>Titles, offices, political posts, honorifics, occupations</item>
            <item>Military, religious, socio-economic terminology</item>
            <item>Dates and month names; age at death on funerary texts</item>
            <item>General keywords, other taxonomies</item>
        </list>
    </div>
    
    <div xml:id="app-allsupp-responsibility">
        <head>Responsibility for this section</head>
        <listBibl>
            <bibl><respStmt><resp>Author</resp><name>Gabriel Bodard</name></respStmt></bibl>
        </listBibl>
    </div>
</div>
